# Lead Details Page Revamp

Revamp the lead details page to optimize space and improve usability by consolidating key actions in the banner and creating focused interactive cards for Instagram and Spotify data.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Spotify playback buttons will use the `rPage` query parameter to navigate through the discography, causing a full page revalidation. This is consistent with current pagination but might feel slightly less "app-like" than a pure client-side state player.

## Proposed Changes

### Banner Section Consolidation

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/kp/Documents/spectral-soundworks-app/src/app/leads/[id]/page.tsx)
- Move **Lead Score**, **Lead Status**, and **Update Profile** button into the `Cinematic Artist Header`.
- Adjust layout to be a multi-row or dense grid within the banner.

### Instagram Card

#### [NEW] [EditableArtistHandle.tsx](file:///c:/Users/kp/Documents/spectral-soundworks-app/src/components/EditableArtistHandle.tsx)
- Create a component similar to `EditableArtistName` but for updating the `instagramHandle`.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/kp/Documents/spectral-soundworks-app/src/app/leads/[id]/page.tsx)
- Implement unified IG card with avatar, handle (editable), followers, and last post status at the top.
- Horizontal scrollable carousel for recent posts below the profile info.

### Spotify Playback Card

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/kp/Documents/spectral-soundworks-app/src/app/leads/[id]/page.tsx)
- Implement "Now Playing" style card.
- Big album art (proxied).
- Track/Album info.
- Playback controls:
    - `Previous` (rPage - 1)
    - `Next` (rPage + 1)
- Release date / Recency text at the bottom.

### Drafts Section

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/kp/Documents/spectral-soundworks-app/src/app/leads/[id]/page.tsx)
- Split drafts into two columns: **Instagram Reachout** and **Email Outreach**.
- If no email is present, IG column takes full width.
- Ensure all "Tune", "Copy", and "Send" functionalities are preserved in each column.

### Activity Timeline

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/kp/Documents/spectral-soundworks-app/src/app/leads/[id]/page.tsx)
- Move to a full-width section at the bottom of the page.

