## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- N/A (UI focused)

### Manual Verification
- Verify layout responsiveness on desktop and mobile.
- Test "Edit Handle" functionality.
- Test Spotify "Next/Previous" buttons and ensure they cycle through the discography correctly.
- Verify that "Update Status" and "Update Profile" in the banner function correctly.
- Check draft columns layout with and without artist emails.
